Log in to the app using your credentials.
Go to the Profile page by tapping on your profile icon or the profile option in the menu.
Locate and tap on the Delete Account button or option available on the Profile page.
Confirm the action when prompted by the app.
Once the account is deleted, your account will be permanently removed. All associated data, including saved progress and preferences, will be deleted automatically from our servers.
Note: This action is irreversible, and the data cannot be recovered once the account is deleted.
